{"tid":529863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台食品印「中國台灣」遭支那國銷毀    一定要標「台灣區」","createTime":"2018-01-15T07:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T11:16:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c72bf6f50ceaab0e8f87aaea6274e71165cd9f71","tid":529863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180115/large/1515979183_718d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180115%2Flarge%2F1515979183_718d.jpg&h=93ce13fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬豪酒店、達美航空等外資，因將港澳台藏等地列為「國家」，引發官民聲討，逼令涉事公司道歉整改。分裂國家成為中共一個不可潛越的紅線，連台灣入口到大陸的食品，也要配合「主旋律」。<br />\n<br />\n過去不少入口大陸的台灣食品只要註名「中國 台灣」便能入口，惟有業界發現近內大陸加大打壓力度，標示「中國台灣」竟被拒絕入口，甚至遇上銷毀的結局，只有「台灣區」、「中國台灣地區」才能過關。<br />\n<br />\n台灣小美冰琪淋、義格實業董事長呂明炎表示，自己去年底接任彰化拓銷協會理事長，至今已接到3宗台灣食品入口大陸被拒的個案。當中全是不知情業界在外包裝採用「產地：中國 台灣」，涉事貨品在福建沿海的平潭、廈門、大嶝三個口岸被截，最終全部被銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n呂明炎表示，過去國民黨執政時期標示「中國台灣」，就可順利入口，惟蔡英文執政，產品便要標示指定字眼。有廠商因「一字之差」而要重新包裝，有人一次損失就是3、400萬元新台幣(約79.3萬至105萬港元)。<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》"},{"pid":"2a44648adf6920d82eb13232d80b4b3822cdc195","tid":529863,"uid":17103,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚好再做大陸啦, 諗下世界啦"},{"pid":"ce32ed6cd0623f175ec5362c21812cee3bca19e0","tid":529863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"中國台灣高雄工業區製造"},{"pid":"3b3f796f21bd967dde6a49e736deecaa51d9171d","tid":529863,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"幾時禁香港參加奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734b8199b9e3069a0c296a60d33c58112a1d8e06","tid":529863,"uid":166893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"大陸越來越癡能線"},{"pid":"50bde07bf0050657677a1635cb269ad57f713319","tid":529863,"uid":34602,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"所以話跟本就唔應該理佢，啲小人你退一步，佢就會進一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabb1b02aef4fe4de40f808fa489287d298b845e","tid":529863,"uid":293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"支那人真係麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74ca110ea359adcb799e164f27531ef9e196c72","tid":529863,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"無得唔理架... <br />\n今年中國玩曬"},{"pid":"5a9d3b8897703a1960493e370cfacc884e764883","tid":529863,"uid":37413,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪霸道囉，其實中國台灣已經好讓步<br />\n而且冇乜問題，係都要乜撚都政治化好討厭"},{"pid":"ede61a92208f0bed5186f888b519051e4bb1fded","tid":529863,"uid":87780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:33:19.000Z","msg":"睇下靠對岸既後果係點啦台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cb943ad712bea6cdf64a91530d3acd53ecc326","tid":529863,"uid":34602,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e74ca110ea359adcb799e164f27531ef9e196c72","tid":529863,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"無得唔理架... <br />\n今年中國玩曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"有時你企硬佢反而縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如印度，緬甸，你比佢認為你好蝦，佢一定會得吋進尺"},{"pid":"45563b341532a856b71751f149d5f5be6d3c370c","tid":529863,"uid":125237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"tw is not a part of china"},{"pid":"9c184b386f1bbedf67b60b62dfeae0858d34b401","tid":529863,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"要没有台灣區食品 <br />\n中國人餓死了"},{"pid":"60becde7e15a145028dd31582724b0dc9bcceeb3","tid":529863,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"對住支那要鬥惡"},{"pid":"150c58caacc1a33251333dcc0879e5610667f957","tid":529863,"uid":9887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"就算迫到人寫台灣省都好<br />\n咪又係精神勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你控制到人軍事內政咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50c85eb1a48e00f4e543c152f08161716a5a6a8","tid":529863,"uid":100208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"橫掂係迫，叫人寫中華人民共和國台灣省先比入境丫嘛，渣㗎"}]}